KEY FEATURES

1.  index.php
    a. shows date in browser title bar
    b. defines frame ratio and page sources
2.  welcome.php
    a. splash page
    b. links to welcome2.php
3.  topframeCD.php
    a. JavaScript for onChange event with pull-down menus
    b. Reset other forms with onClick event
    c. dynamically populated pull-down menus
    d. limit result if string length exceeds 20 chars (adds ellipsis)
    e. string encode/decode for display and queries
    f. browser detection for textbox widths for NN 4.7+
4.  welcome2.php
    a. JavaScript to insert value for sample query
    b. Search form; same as in topframeCD.php
5.  about.php
    a. basic listing of files used and their function
    b. includes the .htaccess and cgis as well
6.  using.php
    a. basic listing of tips and tricks to using phpCDs
    b. also features and db administration
7.  contact.php
    a. uses cdform.cgi for form handling
    b. includes hidden tags for email display purposes
8.  cdlistANY.php
    a. limit result if string length exceeds 35 chars
    b. HR shows after ea. record unless it's the last one
9.  cdlistColumn.php
    a. shows all uniques values for Artist and Album
    b. same result set as the pulldowns but easier to read
10. cdlistSearch.php
    a. main script for doing query
    b. requires explicit use of wildcard character %
11. display.inc
    a. works with cdlistANY.php and cdlistSearch.php
    b. table rows for showing query results
12. zarkobar.inc
    a. displays the title of the project
    b. links to View Cart, Insert/Update, Welcome2.php
13. zarkobar2.inc
    a. shortened version of zarkobar for Add Image popup
    b. title and close window link
14. html_hdr.inc
    a. CSS definition for look and feel
    b. includes all font tags
15. body.inc
    a. standardizes the body tag with marginheight, etc.
16. db_access.inc
    a. basic variables for all db connectivity
    b. DBhost, DBuser, DBpass, DBName, table
17. db_auth.inc
    a. php module for page access authorization
    b. replaced by .htaccess and apache/httpd.conf update
    c. features a single user and password
18. html_end.inc
    a. closing center, body and html tags
    b. keeps things a little tidier
19. apache401.php
    a. replacement for generic apache 401 server error page
    b. can also use the db_auth.inc in lieu of .htaccess
20. cart.php
    a. adds items to the shopping cart
    b. includes the display of the cart too
21. checkout.php
    a. simple form for submitting results for checkout
    b. you can view each records by clicking on id number
22. db.php
    a. sets the session cookie for cart functionality
    b. appends to the table for each session
23. doUpload.php
    a. script behind addImage.php to upload images to server
    b. checks for image as well as correct size and format
24. addImage.php
    a. small popup with form for browsing local drive for images
    b. form to upload images
25. editCDs.php
    a. updates and deletes to database
    b. works with editSearch.php
26. editSearch.php
    a. script used on insert.php for finding records to modify
    b. displays results in an editable format unlike cdlistSearch.php
27. insert.php
    a. main script for adding, updating and deleting database records
    b. uses editSearch.php for finding records to modify
28. cdform.cgi
    a. PERL form handling script used by both the shopping cart and contact forms
    b. sends email to yourname@yourdomain.com with form data
    c. sends an autoresponse to submitter
29. response2.txt
    a. small text file that is added to the autoresponse
    b. this one is specific to the shopping cart form
30. response3.txt
    a. same as response2.txt
    b. this one is specific to the contact form